creator: CACI bv
descriptionHtml: The official student app from Zuyd University of Applied Sciences. Immediately clear overview of your grades and credits; you will be notified when a result is submitted. With this app you can easily register for courses and tests. The feedback from the SLB meetings and issued study advises are also shown in the app.
descriptionShort: Study results, registration for education + tests and (later) your schedule

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We update the app regularly so we can make it better for you. Get the latest version for all of the available OSIRIS features. This version includes several new features, bug fixes and performance improvements. Thanks for using the OSIRIS Student App.
